      "text": "Jo es ſwehtifchu winnu/ un dohſchu tew no winnas weenu Dehlu/ un es ſwehtifchu winnu/ la winnai buhs par dauds Laudim buht/ un dauds Lauschu Rehnini no winnas zelſees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbraäms nomettehs us fawn Waign/ un pafinehjahs/ un fazzija fawa Sirdi: Arrig weenain/ kas ſints Gaddus wezz irr/ weens Behrndsims/ un ar- rig Sara dewiaDefmits Gaddus wezza dsemdehs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbraäms fazzija us Deewu: Kaut jelle Ismaäls ta- wa Preekſchã dſhwotu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Deews fazzija: Ba- teefi Sara tawa Seewa dsein- dehs tew weenu Dehlu/ un tew buhs winna Wahrdn Isaäku faukt/ un es uhszelfchu fawn Derribu ar to/ muhschani par Derribu winna Dſimmunam pehz winnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir Ismaäta labbad eſimu es tew paklausijis/ Reds/ Es eſinu winnu ſwehtijis/ un pa- darrifchu winnu augligu/ un wairofchu winnu warren fohti/ Diwpadeſmits Leeli-Kungi win- nam dsins/ un es eezelfchu win- nu par leelu Tantu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet mannu Derribu zel- ſchu es ar Isaäku/ ko tew Sara noliktã Laika nahkama Gadda dsemdehs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſsch mittejahs ar to runnaht/ un Deews uhskahpe ne Ahbraäma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nehme Ahbraäms to\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Isinaälu fawu Dehlu/ un wiſſu fawa Namnã peedſimmufchus un wiſſus par Naudu pirktus wiſſus no Wihra Kahrtas/ n Ahbraäma Saines/ un apgra fijs tahsPreekſch-Ahdas pee win xo Meeſahn/ tanni paſchã Dee na/ itt ka Deews us winnu bi runnajis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbraäms bija dewin defmits dewix Gaddus wezz kad ta Preekſch-Ahda pee win na Meeſas apgraisita tappe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Isinaäls/ winna Dehls bija trihspadeſmits Gaddu wezz/ kad ta Preekſch-Ahda pe winna Meeſas apgraisita tappe\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tanni paſchã Deen tappa apgraisiti Ahbraäms/ un winna Dehls Ismaäls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſi Wihrã winna Namnã peedſimmufschi/ un pa Naudu pirkti no Swetchinee keem/ tee tappe ar winnu apgra fiti.\n"
    }
